    <h2 class="title">Success Tips: </h2>
    <article>
      <p class="tip">Change Your Shoes </p>
      <ul>
          <li>Avoid walking in shoes that create tension on your joints</li>
          <li>Don't wear shoes that are too tight or loose</li>
          <li>Don't forget to wear clean socks!</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
    <article>
      <p class="tip">Stay Hydrated</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Avoid drinking alcohol and soda before or after your walk.</li>
        <li>Drink plenty of water throughout the day</li>
        <li>Avoid drinking too much water before bed</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
    <article>
      <p class="tip">Wear the right clothes</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Don't wear clothes that are too tight or loose</li>
        <li>Don't wear clothes that restrict airflow or movement</li>
        <li>Consider bringing a change of comfortable or clean clothes</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
